oe=6735D6BB"}, {"file_name": "lawer desk.png", "id": "1021730339243891", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974725_1021730342577224_5121892752200566930_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=u2-S7tQeZdEQ7kNvgFfIb87&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCOjTBFlmEUTMBDv5b2WldlVb5yl3UIUfChyjVQWsMs9Q&oe=6735CB23"}, {"file_name": "certificatemachine.png", "id": "419222644501284", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031359_419222647834617_1044340319385662871_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=gO5dmfID1C8Q7kNvgEDktij&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAPgNDulZHlMfQpuvQ2bmRgHD88liUd7kmhfcDoMrvnTA&oe=6735D647"}, {"file_name": "gustav.png", "id": "1041151010314056", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982712_1041151013647389_9208282846641755977_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=sfPxwts_ZLoQ7kNvgEjB1O8&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDvZZ2cheKf20JYZeMc0WA5XwDx0WELGvMLB4m3WJtr7w&oe=6735DBB1"}, {"file_name": "lawyers head-resize.png", "id": "409356922173502", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984472_409356925506835_675175198628609171_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4ZLbhkIWtQQQ7kNvgGad5c0&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDEc7Wh-1bKPoRl5jmyaSEwj75KQj_6_QIJqevX086osQ&oe=6735E9EF"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "1568747630685050", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031482_1568747634018383_5207621578584535018_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Oa3INWdAWpMQ7kNvgH9WiOV&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAk1vNGgy2kCMZoLpDYREseb1ag4YqvnTBPXcyE7iJzqg&oe=6735C889"}, "display_name": "Metamorphosis", "keywords": ["bug", "meta", "puzzle", "escape", "mystery"], "long_description": "# **An Extraordinary Journey Through a Surreal World**\n\n---\n\nIf navigating daily life in 1900s Vienna isn\u2019t complicated enough for Gregor, things take a truly Kafkaesque turn one morning when he awakens to discover he\u2019s been transformed into... a **cockroach**.\n\n### Armed with only your **wit** and **strange new appendages**, embark on a mind-bending journey to unravel the mystery behind your *metamorphosis*.\n\n### \n\n### **Welcome to a World Unlike Any Other**\n\nIn this surreal world, everyday objects loom like towering giants, while dizzying heights challenge your step, and each turn begins a new adventure.\n\n\n#### What to expect:\n- **Dance** all night in a bug's nightclub  \n- **Delve** into arthropod-organized crime  \n- **Dodge** the hands of mammoth humans  \n- **Escape** the bureaucratic traps of buggy officials\n\n---\n\n**But beware**, your friend\u2019s life is hanging by a thread, and your only hope to regain human form lies deep within the heart of a mysterious **Tower**\u2014a place with its own plans for you.\n\n---\n\n### Metamorphosis is a first-person **adventure-platformer** set in a surreal, beautifully twisted world, where your newfound abilities as an insect are your only hope for redemption.\n### \nWill you **avoid the Tower** and **save your friend**? Or will you be **lost forever** in this strange, curious land?\n\n---\n\n# *Embrace the challenge. Escape the Tower. Your metamorphosis awaits.*\n", "short_description": "If navigating daily life in 1900s Vienna isn\u2019t complicated enough for Gregor, things take a Kafkaesque turn one morning when he awakens to discover he\u2019s transformed into a cockroach. Armed with only your wits and some strange new appendages, set off on an extraordinary journey to unravel the mystery of your metamorphosis. \n\nMetamorphosis is a first-person adventure set in a surreal world filled with strange and curious denizens where your newfound abilities are your only hope for redemption."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": 